   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Didymus ..., Thsaphibis, ... of Harpalus ..., Harmiysis, son of Harmiysis ..., Psosneus alias ..., Psosneus son of Petenou( ), for poll-tax 45 drachmas 3 obols, for dike-tax 6 drachmas 4 obols. Heraclas, son of Centaurus, for poll-tax 45 drachmas 3 obols, for dike-tax 6 drachmas 4 obols. The same person for the city of Oxyrhynchus for poll-tax 16 drachmas, for dike-tax 13 drachmas 2 obols. The fourth year of Nero Claudius Caesar Augustus Germanicus Imperator, the 21st of the month Sebastos.</ab>
